Work Order Estimation

Estimate Field Service Work Before You Create Work Orders

Improve customer satisfaction by enabling your users to provide your customers with a quote and an estimate of the work to be done associated with a specific asset. Users can generate quotes for assets based on work types and necessary products.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Automotive Cloud, Communications Cloud, Energy and Utilities Cloud, and Manufacturing Cloud.

Who: This feature is available to users with the Work Order Estimation permission set.

How: You can launch the work order estimation process from an account, an asset, or an existing work order. Define the work to be done on the quote by providing details, review the quote summary, generate a proposal, and create work orders after customer approval.
title: Estimate Field Service Work Before Creating Work Orders
